Here’s a neat and clean README for your basic sign-up form website:

📝 Sign-Up Form Website
A simple and responsive sign-up form built with HTML and CSS. This form allows users to create an account by entering their personal details and accepting terms and conditions.
🚀 Features
- Clean and modern UI
- Input fields for:
- Name
- Email
- Password
- Confirm Password
- Terms & Conditions checkbox
- Register button
- Login link for existing users
📸 Preview
Sign-Up Form Screenshot
Replace with actual image path if hosting the screenshot.
🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
📂 File Structure
/project-root
│
├── index.html       # Main HTML file
├── style.css        # Styling for the form
└── README.md        # Project documentation


📋 How to Use
- Clone the repository:
git clone 
- Open index.html in your browser.
- Customize styles or form behavior as needed.
✅ Future Enhancements
- Add form validation using JavaScript
- Integrate with backend for user registration
- Improve accessibility and mobile responsiveness
